<![CDATA[<div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: x-small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Please do not respond to this email. This email was sent from an unattended mailbox, and replies are not reviewed. Please instead contact your Staffing representative on&nbsp;</b><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1"><span style="line-height: 18px;"><b>{!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}</b></span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: x-small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="line-height: 18px;"><br></span></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Dear&nbsp;</font><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Job_placement__c.Contact_Name__c}</font><font face="Arial, sans-serif">,</font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: small;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">I hope you have enjoyed your placement on NCS with The Challenge on one of our pilot programmes. &nbsp;</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">This payment email is regarding your work on NCS: Real Challenge Action. You will receive up to four emails in total, each corresponding to a specific NCS: Real Challenge Action day. &nbsp;</font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">This payment email is regarding your work on NCS: Real Challenge Action on&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: small; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><b>{!Job_placement__c.Assignment_start_date__c}<font color="#ff0000">&nbsp;</font></b><font face="arial">for</font></font><font style="font-size: small;">&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: small;"><font face="arial">{!Job_placement__c.Wave__c}.</font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: small;"><font color="#ff0000"><br></font></span></div></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Your gross pay for completing this day is&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!Job_placement__c.Total_Amount_to_Pay__c}</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">. This is subject to Tax and National&nbsp;Insurance contributions.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">You will receive this on {!Job_placement__c.Payroll_payment_date__c}.</span></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: small;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: small;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">On your payslip (sent via email on {!Job_placement__c.Payroll_payment_date__c}) , you will see the total amount and breakdown of payment which you will receive for the entire wave.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="font-size: 13.333333015441895px;">Due to new auto-enrolment legislation, employees of The Challenge, including summer staff, will be automatically enrolled in a workplace pension scheme. This is a way of saving for your retirement that's arranged by your employer. This affects staff who earn more than Â£473 per month and are aged between 22 and state pension age. You will see your pension contributions on your payslip. For further information, please go to&nbsp;<a href="http://www.gov.uk/workplace-pensions" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">www.gov.uk/workplace-<wbr>pensions</a>.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="font-size: 13.333333015441895px;"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="font-size: 13.333333015441895px;">Further communications</font><span style="font-size: 13.333333015441895px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">, including how to opt out,</span><span style="font-size: 13.333333015441895px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;will be sent to you in September where we will start to process all summer staff for auto-enrolment. At that point, i</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 13.333333015441895px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">f you would like to opt out of the pension scheme, you will need an opt-out form from The People's Pension, which you can get from and then return to by emailing&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:thepeoplespension@bandce.co.uk" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); font-size: 13.333333015441895px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">thepeoplespension@<wbr>bandce.co.uk</a><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 13.333333015441895px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 13.333333015441895px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">Staff will have a one month opt-out period: this begins from the day the administration for their becoming a member is complete, i.e. one month from the date of enrolment, which will not take place until September</span></div></div></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: small;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: small;"><br></div></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Yours sincerely,</font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: center;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><font size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><br clear="none" style="line-height: 18px;"></font><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="line-height: 18px;">{!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}</span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="line-height: 18px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="line-height: 18px;">CR 4.2.4b</span></font></div>]]></td>
